<title>AUSTRALIA: RTRS-BHP in A$636 million share issue.</title>
<headline>RTRS-BHP in A$636 million share issue.</headline>
<dateline>MELBOURNE 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Broken Hill Pty Co Ltd (BHP), Australia's largest company, said on Thursday it would raise up to A$636 million from a non-renounceable issue of not more than 36.55 million shares.</p>
